I have had many instances where crystal clear EVPs I have recorded 
have often been heard by myself and others several times, only to be 
reviewed again and suddenly no longer heard. 

In agreement with Frank, sometimes there are voices I hear, messages 
that come through in my recordings that no one else can hear at all. 
I have always known these messages were meant for me, and I am 
grateful to have had the privilege of the communication. 

April S.

